  <brief_title>Sore Throat Prevention Following Intubation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison Between Xylocaine Gel as Endotracheal Cuff Lubricant Versus Dexamethasone 8 mg Intravenously or Both for Sore Throat Prevention Following Intubation: Interventional Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
